    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>natural yoghurt </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) with your <strong>curry powder</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp</span>] <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil</strong> in a bowl</p><p>Add the <strong>paneer cubes</strong> and mix well until they're completely coated – this is your <strong>coated paneer</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
