      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cover a baking tray with <strong>tin foil</strong> (to avoid mess!)</p><p>Add the <strong>coated paneer</strong> to the baking tray and put it under the grill for<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>4-5 min or until the paneer is starting to char – this is your <strong>tandoori paneer</strong></p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3 or more? You may need to do this in batches!</p>",
