      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut your <strong>cucumber</strong> in half lengthways</p><p>Scrape out the<strong> inner seeds </strong>with a teaspoon and set aside for later, then dice the rest</p><p>Peel and chop your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Dice your <strong>tomato[es]</strong></p>",
